flowchart LR
    User[Developer in terminal]
    Host[Host project workspace]
    PiCLI[pi coding-agent CLI]
    AgentSession[AgentSession runtime]
    AgentCore[pi-agent-core Agent and loop]
    PiAI[pi-ai provider API]
    Provider[LLM provider or OAuth subscription]
    Tools[Local read bash edit write grep find ls tools]
    Extensions[Extensions skills prompts themes packages]
    Sessions[JSONL session store]
    TUI[pi-tui interactive renderer]
    RPC[JSON or RPC integrations]
    Sandbox[Optional container VM micro-VM or OpenShell]

    User --> PiCLI
    PiCLI --> AgentSession
    AgentSession --> AgentCore
    AgentCore --> PiAI
    PiAI --> Provider
    AgentCore --> Tools
    Tools --> Host
    AgentSession --> Sessions
    AgentSession --> Extensions
    PiCLI --> TUI
    PiCLI --> RPC
    Sandbox -. optional isolation .- PiCLI
    Sandbox -. optional tool routing .- Tools
